commit_message:
Update force-detach interface

The force detach interface is used for nova bdm is deleted,
but storage cluster attach and cinder volume_attachment exist.

Currently, the force-detach interface has not very appropriate
current is:
{
    "os-force_detach": {
        "attachment_id": "d8777f54-84cf-4809-a679-468ffed56cf1",
        "connector": {
            "initiator": "iqn.2012-07.org.fake:01"
        }
    }
}
the attachment_id and connecor are optional parameters, but when
volume is multiattach and attached to more than one instance. we
can not identify detach which attachment. so it should be changed
as fllows
{
    "os-force_detach": {
        "attachment_id": "d8777f54-84cf-4809-a679-468ffed56cf1"
    }
}
If multiattach volume and attachted to more than one instance the
attachment_id is need.

